    "h1": { "en": "Frame", "zh": "框架" },
    "lede": { "en": "Aluminum extrusions, T-nuts, brackets, and bumpers form the mechanical chassis everything else bolts onto. Squareness built in here governs every motion downstream.", "zh": "铝型材、T 型螺母、角码和橡胶脚垫一起组成机械底座，后面所有零件都装在它上面。框架在这一步装得正不正，直接决定了之后所有运动准不准。" }
  },
